-- US Citizen Kidnapped in Nigeria’s Delta Region, Police Say
-- B y   E m e l e   O n u
-- 2012-01-21T10:51:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-21/us-citizen-kidnapped-in-nigeria-s-delta-region-police-say.html
A U.S. citizen was kidnapped
yesterday in Warri,  Nigeria ’s oil-rich southern Delta region,
authorities said.  “He works for Marubal Engineering in Sapele and traveled
to Warri where he was trailed and kidnapped,” Charles Muka, a
police spokesman, said today by phone from Warri.  Police have received information that the kidnappers are
demanding 50 million naira ($310,000) ransom, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emele Onu in Lagos at 
